%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=8a435e4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/juneforstfuneral&gt;</a><br />\n<br />\n想喺不久將來見證條例真正撒回？<br />\n想所有受誣告嘅義士被撒銷控罪？<br />\n想未來依然能夠光明正大喺條街，<br />\n大聲屌鳩港共正苦老母都無人拉？<br />\n麻煩各位喺呢場抗爭馬拉松繼續跑落去。<br />\n<br />\n終點未至，未可中止。<br />\n自己香港，自己救。"},{"pid":"30c14046e4baacd669abb2e777dd8c5363795a23","tid":1261234,"uid":133424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EP5a29a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEP5a29a.png&h=0bb69e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻狗改咗名"},{"pid":"2a0768471176d1a9f7b4193888833a3b1af5a47b","tid":1261234,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5402e74ec624334c06aa228d2b23c2821a5dc5df","tid":1261234,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"淨係知佢係黑警，但係點解話佢係清泉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1qqR2z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1qqR2z.png&h=01fac7e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8251d78a2795b0e276a09ff9a093358e17e3ee95","tid":1261234,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a0768471176d1a9f7b4193888833a3b1af5a47b","tid":1261234,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5402e74ec624334c06aa228d2b23c2821a5dc5df","tid":1261234,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"淨係知佢係黑警，但係點解話佢係清泉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1qqR2z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1qqR2z.png&h=01fac7e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:00:43.000Z","msg":"佢係咪仆街死咗？佢咁樣算唔算宣布佢會自殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/s